## Find arctan(8/10)   {2}

$$arctan = tan^{-1}(8/10) = 38.659 = 38\degree$$

## Find arctan(-8/10)   {2}

$$arctan = tan^{-1}(-8/10) = 360\degree - 38\degree= 322\degree$$

