$$kcos(p) = 9$$

$$ksin(p) = 9$$

$$tan p = 9/9$$

$$9 sin(x+45\degree) $$

$$p = tan^{-1} (9/9) = 45\degree$$

$$k = 9^{2} + 9^{2} =162\degree$$

