## Form the Augmented Matrix {1}

$$aug(A) = \left[\begin{matrix}10&10&1&171\\9&8&10&153\\9&7&5&138\\\end{matrix}\right]$$

## Use Row Operations so this is in Row Echelon form {3}

$$\frac{1}{10}⋅R1→R1$$

$$\left[\begin{matrix}1&1&\frac{1}{10}&\frac{171}{10}\\9&8&10&153\\9&7&5&138\\\end{matrix}\right]$$

$$1/9⋅R2→R2$$

$$\left[\begin{matrix}1&1&\frac{1}{10}&\frac{171}{10}\\1&\frac{8}{9}&\frac{10}{9}&17\\9&7&5&138\\\end{matrix}\right]$$

$$\frac{1}{9}⋅R3→R3$$

$$\left[\begin{matrix}1&1&\frac{1}{10}&\frac{171}{10}\\1&\frac{8}{9}&\frac{10}{9}&17\\1&\frac{7}{9}&\frac{5}{9}&\frac{46}{3}\\\end{matrix}\right]$$

$$R2-1⋅R1→R2$$

$$\left[\begin{matrix}1&1&\frac{1}{10}&\frac{171}{10}\\1&\frac{8}{9}&\frac{10}{9}&17\\1&\frac{7}{9}&\frac{5}{9}&\frac{46}{3}\\\end{matrix}\right]$$

$$R3-1⋅R1→R3$$

$$\left[\begin{matrix}1&1&\frac{1}{10}&\frac{171}{10}\\0&-\frac{1}{9}&\frac{91}{90}&-\frac{1}{10}\\0&-\frac{2}{9}&\frac{41}{90}&-\frac{53}{30}\\\end{matrix}\right]$$

$$-9⋅R2→R2$$

$$\left[\begin{matrix}1&1&\frac{1}{10}&\frac{171}{10}\\0&1&-\frac{91}{10}&\frac{9}{10}\\0&-\frac{2}{9}&\frac{41}{90}&-\frac{53}{30}\\\end{matrix}\right]$$

$$-\frac{9}{2}⋅R3→R3$$

$$\left[\begin{matrix}1&1&\frac{1}{10}&\frac{171}{10}\\0&1&-\frac{91}{10}&\frac{9}{10}\\0&1&\frac{41}{90}&\frac{159}{20}\\\end{matrix}\right]$$

$$R3-1⋅R2→R3$$

$$\left[\begin{matrix}1&1&\frac{1}{10}&\frac{171}{10}\\0&1&-\frac{91}{10}&\frac{9}{10}\\0&0&\frac{141}{20}&\frac{141}{20}\\\end{matrix}\right]$$

$$\frac{20}{141}⋅R3→R3$$

$$\left[\begin{matrix}1&1&\frac{1}{10}&\frac{171}{10}\\0&1&-\frac{91}{10}&\frac{9}{10}\\0&0&1&1\\\end{matrix}\right]$$

$$R2+91/10⋅R3→R2$$

$$\left[\begin{matrix}1&1&\frac{1}{10}&\frac{171}{10}\\0&1&0&10\\0&0&1&1\\\end{matrix}\right]$$

$$R1-1/10⋅R3→R1$$

$$\left[\begin{matrix}1&1&0&17\\0&1&0&10\\0&0&1&1\\\end{matrix}\right]$$

$$R1-1⋅R2→R1$$

$$\left[\begin{matrix}1&0&0&7\\0&1&0&10\\0&0&1&1\\\end{matrix}\right]$$

## Hence find x in the equation Ax = b {2}

$$Ax = b = \left[\begin{matrix}10&10&1\\9&8&10\\9&7&5\\\end{matrix}\right] ⋅ \left[\begin{matrix}7\\10\\1\\\end{matrix}\right] = \left[\begin{matrix}171\\153\\138\\\end{matrix}\right] $$

